<category>
      <pattern>architecture</pattern>
      <template>
 The construction of the Taj Mahal started in 1631 and ended in 1653. The architecture is a combination of Persian Islamic and Indian styles. Ustad Ahmad Lahauri was the architect of Taj Mahal. 30 different varieties of semi precious and precious stones were used and is perfectly symmetrical in every way except for the two tombs.
      </template>
