<template>
Around 1000 elephants were employed for the transportation of construction material.
The construction cost of this masterpiece monument was around Rs.320 million.
Many types of marbles used were brought from China, Afghanistan, Sri lanka and Arabia.
In recent times, different studies suggest that the Taj Mahal is sinking in the Yamuna river.
